Girlfriend almost left me

Never should have bet against me

snippet.textDisplay:
I don't know why I look at these people,
Cant find my way to the church steeple.
The feelings inside run so deep,
They approach like a disease they feel so steep.
The words I speak I hope to never repeat,
Inside I'm broken, confused - I feel defeat.
The world has gone crazy in my eyes,
Like women who never want the nice guys.
I pump up my ego and try to be confident,
But never in my days do I feel anyone will make a dent.
Im just trying to live my life and make a cent,
I wish my heart could feel innocent.
The guilt of the pain I have caused those around,
You may as well believe that I will always be profound.
Do you think that the words you read,
Are not the words inside which make my soul bleed?
Im not playing games anymore because I know what I want in life,
I'll never let anyone break my strife.
If you think I'm a quitter then think twice,
The hole in my heart is only something that will splice.
When I seek you out it is for a reason,
I have no reason to give your heart treason.
I wish to love and feel love forever more,
Deny this gift if you wish but it only makes you poor.
The rich will embellish the generosity,
Live your life so you may be free.
I will be here for the person who will love me,
Until then you can guarantee.
I am a lover in my heart.
